---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions - TaxPortal" description="TaxPortal terms and conditions of use.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-canvas dark:bg-primary">
    <main class="min-h-screen">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">Terms and Conditions</h1>
        
        <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-6 text-body dark:text-muted">
          <p>By accessing or using TaxPortal, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use this website.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Use of Service</h2>
          <p>TaxPortal provides free access to tax information and calculators. You agree to use these tools for personal, non-commercial purposes only.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>All information and calculations on TaxPortal are for general informational purposes only and do not constitute professional tax advice. We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of any content.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>All content on TaxPortal, including text, graphics, logos, and software, is the property of TaxPortal or its licensors and is protected by intellectual property laws.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>TaxPortal shall not be liable for any damages arising from the use of, or inability to use, our services. This includes but is not limited to direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms and Conditions at any time. Continued use of TaxPortal following changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
